 >The real challenge for the legendary Knights will lie in the epic bosses and their corrupted variations. From the Royal Phalanx to the Plague Bringer, Praxis will summon anything in his power to stop you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try different builds, upgrade your Ember Tree, and don't fear death. Persistence will be your key to victory! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135230/extras/0c7ffa820bfb4731c28af4fe2d3ba2b6.poster.avif?t=1773667492\" width=780 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135230/extras/0c7ffa820bfb4731c28af4fe2d3ba2b6.webm?t=1773667492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135230/extras/0c7ffa820bfb4731c28af4fe2d3ba2b6.mp4?t=1773667492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ember Knights FREE Update Features:</strong>  <br> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Daily Dungeon game mode </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Boss Rush mode </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Chaos Run mode </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 adorable pets: Ember Dog & Ember Cat </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135230/extras/2afc2104dcd98cfacf2e36be08ae47fe.poster.avif?t=1773667492\" width=618 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1135230/extras/2afc2104dcd98cfacf2e36be08ae47fe.webm?t=177